  "description": "This repository captures the end-to-end plan for delivering a production-grade, Node.jsâ€“based API Gateway for PocketLOL. The gateway will act as the single public ingress, handling authentication, rate limiting, routing, protocol mediation, and edge-friendly response shaping while remaining stateless and container-ready.",
